            <p style="text-align: left;">(2) Despite our greatest efforts, a small number of products in our catalog may be incorrectly priced. We will check the prices when we process your order and before charging the payment. If a product is incorrectly priced and the correct price is higher than the price on the website, we will contact you before shipping the goods to ask if you would like to purchase the product at the correct price or cancel the order. If the correct price of a product is lower than the price stated by us, we will charge the lower amount and send you the product.</p>
